Product Description

The classic 80’s PUMA California has been brought back as a must need retro sneaker. Originally a laid-back training sneaker, the California is now an on trend streetwear style.

PUMA is the global athletic brand that successfully fuses influences from sport, lifestyle and fashion. PUMA's unique industry perspective delivers the unexpected in sport-lifestyle footwear, apparel and accessories, through technical innovation and revolutionary design.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice shoes
Reviewed in the United States 🇺🇸 on September 10, 2022
Size: 9.5Color: White/BlackVerified Purchase
Sharp looking shoe. I have received many compliments. It is decent for people with wider feet or any type of feet really. It’s not the most comfortable or supportive shoe, but the look makes up for it. The sole is a little hard. I only wear them on short outings right now, but I’m still breaking mine in. The size is pretty true to size, but if you have wider feet, you may want to consider going a half size up for more comfort. They do kind of squeeze your toes. Go ahead, get you a pair. They will look great on you!! Enjoy.

sofia g
4.0 out of 5 stars A little stiff an narrow
Reviewed in the United States 🇺🇸 on July 12, 2022
Size: 8.5Color: Whisper White-puma W 1769Verified Purchase
I bought size 8.5 because it is the size I wear and the feedback indicated that it should fit me well. It is a shoe with a beautiful combination of colors, I am not a fan of the brand but I am always willing to try brands and this time I allowed myself to buy some comfortable shoes to wear with different styles.
The front shape is somewhat strange, maybe it's just that I'm not used to this model, it looks like a duck head. Something that is very important to me is that the leather is not too stiff, this one is quite stiff, in addition, the model is for a narrow foot (very narrow), my foot is not wide but roomy shoes are better for me.
This model is quite narrow, it is felt especially in the front part where the laces start, my toes fell asleep in a couple of hours and without wearing socks, I will need very thin socks or I will simply wear them without socks. The sole is quite comfortable, although a bit stiff.
After all, you can see the good material and they look durable, despite everything, I hope they soften with some use, I really trust that hahahaha
